title: Adobe CS3 ME  Middle East
description:
These are all of Adobe's CS3 products for the Middle East, as developed by Winsoft.
I packaged all these together since Adobe's Middle East cracked products were so hard to find and wanted to share
everyone with it.

Middle East products included in this release:

* Acrobat 8 Proffesional Hebrew Version
* Photoshop CS3 Middle East
* Illustrator CS3 Middle East
* InDesign CS3 Middle East
* Dreamweaver CS3 Middle East
* InCopy CS3 Middle East

Non Middle-East products included in this release:
(these products do not have ME versions. However, I have included them in order to create a more complete package):

* Flash CS3
* FireWorks CS3
